properties.description: The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: byte_length
properties.description: • byte_length - (Required) The number of random bytes to produce. The minimum value is 1, which produces eight bits of randomness.

properties.name: keepers
properties.description: • keepers - (Optional) Arbitrary map of values that, when changed, will trigger a new id to be generated. See the main provider documentation for more information.

properties.name: prefix
properties.description: • prefix - (Optional) Arbitrary string to prefix the output value with. This string is supplied as-is, meaning it is not guaranteed to be URL-safe or base64 encoded.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: min
properties.description: • min - (int) The minimum inclusive value of the range.

properties.name: max
properties.description: • max - (int) The maximum inclusive value of the range.

properties.name: keepers
properties.description: • keepers - (Optional) Arbitrary map of values that, when changed, will trigger a new id to be generated. See the main provider documentation for more information.

properties.name: seed
properties.description: • seed - (Optional) A custom seed to always produce the same value.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: keepers
properties.description: • keepers - (Optional) Arbitrary map of values that, when changed, will trigger a new id to be generated. See the main provider documentation for more information.

properties.name: length
properties.description: • length - (Optional) The length (in words) of the pet name.

properties.name: prefix
properties.description: • prefix - (Optional) A string to prefix the name with.

properties.name: separator
properties.description: • separator - (Optional) The character to separate words in the pet name.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: input
properties.description: • input - (Required) The list of strings to shuffle.

properties.name: result_count
properties.description: • result_count - (Optional) The number of results to return. Defaults to the number of items in the input list. If fewer items are requested, some elements will be excluded from the result. If more items are requested, items will be repeated in the result but not more frequently than the number of items in the input list.

properties.name: keepers
properties.description: • keepers - (Optional) Arbitrary map of values that, when changed, will trigger a new id to be generated. See the main provider documentation for more information.

properties.name: seed
properties.description: • seed - (Optional) Arbitrary string with which to seed the random number generator, in order to produce less-volatile permutations of the list. Important: Even with an identical seed, it is not guaranteed that the same permutation will be produced across different versions of Terraform. This argument causes the result to be less volatile, but not fixed for all time.
The following arguments are supported:

properties.name: length
properties.description: • length - (Required) The length of the string desired

properties.name: upper
properties.description: • upper - (Optional) (default true) Include uppercase alphabet characters in random string.

properties.name: min_upper
properties.description: • min_upper - (Optional) (default 0) Minimum number of uppercase alphabet characters in random string.

properties.name: lower
properties.description: • lower - (Optional) (default true) Include lowercase alphabet characters in random string.

properties.name: min_lower
properties.description: • min_lower - (Optional) (default 0) Minimum number of lowercase alphabet characters in random string.

properties.name: number
properties.description: • number - (Optional) (default true) Include numeric characters in random string.

properties.name: min_numeric
properties.description: • min_numeric - (Optional) (default 0) Minimum number of numeric characters in random string.

properties.name: special
properties.description: • special - (Optional) (default true) Include special characters in random string. These are !@#$%&*()-_=+[]{}<>:?

properties.name: min_special
properties.description: • min_special - (Optional) (default 0) Minimum number of special characters in random string.

properties.name: override_special
properties.description: • override_special - (Optional) Supply your own list of special characters to use for string generation. This overrides the default character list in the special argument. The special argument must still be set to true for any overwritten characters to be used in generation.

properties.name: keepers
